OL,3,CScottish Government abandons 2030
OL,4,Cclimate change target
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government has confirmed
OL,7,Fit is ditching a climate change target
OL,8,Fto reduce emissions by 75% by 2030,
OL,9,Fbut maintains it still intends to meet
OL,10,Fa 2045 net zero goal.
OL,12,FThe move came in response to a report
OL,13,Fpublished last month by the
OL,14,Findependent Climate Change Committee
OL,15,F(CCC) that said Scotland was too far
OL,16,Fbehind meeting the target, making it
OL,17,Fno longer credible.
OL,19,FThe Scottish Government has missed
OL,20,Feight of the last 12 yearly targets on
OL,21,Femissions.
