OL,4,Cclimate change target
OL,6,FAddressing Holyrood on Thursday, Net
OL,7,FZero Secretary Mairi McAllan said she
OL,8,Faccepted the CCC's criticism but lay
OL,9,Fthe blame at the feet of Rishi Sunak's
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,FShe was also forced to apologise after
OL,13,Felements of her environmental
OL,14,Fstatement were reported by the media
OL,15,Fahead of its delivery in the Scottish
OL,16,FParliament.
