OL,3,CScottish Government abandons 2030
OL,4,Cclimate change target
OL,6,FMs McAllan told MSPs: "In this
OL,7,Fchallenging context of cuts, UK
OL,8,Fbacktracking, we accept the Climate
OL,9,FChange Committee's recent re-
OL,10,Farticulation that this parliament's
OL,11,Finterim 2030 target is out of reach.
OL,13,F"We must now act to chart a course to
OL,14,F2045 at a pace and scale that is
OL,15,Ffeasible, fair and just.
OL,26,@nD@WOU
