OL,6,F"With this in mind, I can today
OL,7,Fconfirm that, working with parliament
OL,8,Fon a timetable, the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment will bring forward
OL,10,Fexpedited legislation to address
OL,11,Fmatters raised by the Climate Change
OL,12,FCommittee, and ensure our legislative
OL,13,Fframework better reflects the reality
OL,14,Fof long-term climate policymaking.
OL,16,F"The narrowly drawn Bill will retain
OL,17,Four legal commitment to 2045 alongside
OL,18,Fannual reporting on progress, while
OL,19,Fintroducing a target approach based on
OL,20,Ffive-yearly carbon budgets."
