OL,6,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,7,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,8,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,9,Fdominating the political agenda...
OL,11,FSpeaking earlier during First
OL,12,FMinister's Questions, Humza Yousaf did
OL,13,Fnot dispute that the interim target
OL,14,Fwill be scrapped.
OL,16,FInstead, he reaffirmed his
OL,17,Fgovernment's commitment to achieving
OL,18,Fnet zero by 2045.
