OL,6,F"This government will not move back by
OL,7,Fa single month, a week or even a day
OL,8,Ffrom that 2045 target for achieving
OL,9,Fnet zero," he said.
OL,11,F"Let's be clear, the CCC were always
OL,12,Fclear with us that the 2030 target was
OL,13,Fa stretch target. That was clear to
OL,14,Fall of us when we all committed, we
OL,15,Fall backed that target in the first
OL,16,Fplace.
OL,18,F"But what doesn't change, and what
OL,19,Fwon't change, is that end destination
OL,20,Fof 2045."
