OL,6,FAs part of that, Ms McAllan announced
OL,7,Fa "new package of climate action
OL,8,Fmeasures", pledging the Scottish
OL,9,FGovernment would work to treble the
OL,10,Fnumber of charging points available
OL,11,Ffor electric vehicles, in a bid to
OL,12,Fencourage more people to switch away
OL,13,Ffrom petrol and diesel.
OL,15,FThis could lead to approximately
OL,16,F24,000 additional charge points being
OL,17,Finstalled across the country by 2030,
OL,18,Fthe Net Zero Secretary added.
