OL,6,FAnd to encourage more people to ditch
OL,7,Fcars, she added the government would
OL,8,F"explore a new national integrated
OL,9,Fticketing system for public transport
OL,10,Fin Scotland".
OL,12,FPromising pilot projects to reduce
OL,13,Femissions from agriculture and
OL,14,Faccelerate peatland restoration, Ms
OL,15,FMcAllan insisted there was "no doubt
OL,16,Fabout the seriousness with which this
OL,17,Fgovernment treats the climate and
OL,18,Fnature crisis".
