OL,6,FHowever, she said the "severe
OL,7,Fbudgetary restrictions imposed by the
OL,8,FUK government" and the "continuing
OL,9,Fconstraints of devolution", meant the
OL,10,FScottish Government was trying to
OL,11,F"deliver societal and economic
OL,12,Ftransformation with one hand tied
OL,13,Fbehind our back".
OL,15,FAnd she warned "full delivery" of the
OL,16,FScottish Government's plans would
OL,17,Fdepend on Westminster "reversing the
OL,18,F9% cut to our capital budget".
