OL,6,FThe Scottish Conservatives said
OL,7,Fscrapping the interim goal will be an
OL,8,F"abject humiliation" for the SNP and
OL,9,FGreen Government at Holyrood.
OL,11,FNet zero spokesman Douglas Lumsden
OL,12,Fsaid: "For all the boasting about
OL,13,Ftheir supposed environmental
OL,14,Fcredentials, the reality is a
OL,15,Fsuccession of missed targets ` and
OL,16,Fbeing forced to throw in the towel on
OL,17,Fthis flagship pledge represents the
OL,18,Fbiggest failure of the lot.
